<br>
Just wanted to know how mages can avoid getting killed by adds when they are soloing.<br>
<br>
As in, you and GobanerjoberGoner are killing a single spawn in a dungeon, and a mob walks up from behind you and starts hitting.<br>
<br>
What can you do lvls 1-50?  50-65?  From the outset, it looks like mages are seriously lacking self preservation skills (probably by design).  What can you do?<br>
<br>
