These items are good for defense to a point.<br>
<br>
Crystalline silk nets: 2 charges of ensnaring root.<br>
Wooly Spider net: 3 charges of ensnaring root.<br>
Forlorn totem of Rolfon Zek: 3 charges of holy might (stun).<br>
Scepter of the Forlorn: 10 charges of clinging darkness.<br>
Ball of Burlap Yarn: 3 charges of snare.<br>
Bioluminescent Orb: Infinite Blinding luminescence.<br>
